; 
<bibRefCitation author="Hobbs &amp; Lilly" box="[711,940,1540,1565]" firstAuthor="Hobbs" pageId="111" pageNumber="112" pagination="453 - 462" refId="ref90432" refString="Hobbs, G. A. &amp; Lilly, C. E. (1954) Ecology of species of Megachile Latreille in the mixed prairie region of southern Alberta with special reference to pollination of alfalfa. Ecology, 35, 453 - 462. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 1931035" type="journal article" year="1954">Hobbs &amp; Lilly 1954</bibRefCitation>
